<div class="nr_title" id="nr_title">
 第243章 明哲保身此行旨 兄弟再逢相见欢
</div>
<div class="nr_page">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tbody><tr>
<td class="prev"><script>document.writeln("<a id='pt_prev' href='\/wap\/login.html?url=" +  encodeURIComponent(document.URL) + "'><font>加入书签<\/font><\/a>")</script><a id="pt_prev" href="/wap/login.html?url=http%3A%2F%2Fm.bqg5200.com%2Fwapbook-6935-4330773%2F"><font>加入书签</font></a>
